{"tid":607889,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[ 認真討論中文 ] 歐式中文例子","createTime":"2018-03-27T16:03:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-07T06:25:53.000Z","uid":54337,"like":160,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"be75bfdd22758aaf1d0d6cc28d6dc3f25c754742","tid":607889,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T16:03:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/27/233859_2b277949b5f1115380e108766089812f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F27%2F233859_2b277949b5f1115380e108766089812f.png&h=50211bad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第一，&ldquo;部分連登會員，對肥絲大隻進行完全封鎖&rdquo; (共17個字)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>&ldquo; 進行完全封鎖 &rdquo;</strong></span></span><br />\n我想問，呢啲係乜撚野中文？<br />\n如果俾我落筆，簡簡單單咁寫：<br />\n&ldquo;部分連登會員，完全封鎖肥絲大隻&rdquo; (共14個字)<br />\n咁咪得囉。<br />\n中文最緊要簡潔精簡。<br />\n<br />\n進行調查，進行研究 .....<br />\n調查就調查，研究就研究，<br />\n乜撚野叫做進行調查  進行研究。<br />\n<br />\n呢啲垃圾中文，累贅而且多餘。<br />\n進行乜，進行物，係典型歐西式垃圾中文。<br />\n<br />\n第二，&ldquo;其實&rdquo; = 英文 exactly。<br />\n文中 &ldquo;其實&rdquo; 呢兩個字，多餘到爆。<br />\n縱使刪除&ldquo;其實&rdquo;兩個字，該句句子意思都無變到。<br />\n<br />\n第三，歐西式中文特點之一，係死唔斷氣。<br />\n一堆字密密麻麻，睇撚死人。<br />\n<br />\n個 &ldquo;在&rdquo; 字，同個 &ldquo;讓&rdquo; 字中間，好心就落個逗號啦，睇撚死人咩。<br />\n<br />\n你地自己數下，<br />\n由個 &ldquo;其&rdquo; 字，到個 &ldquo;啊&rdquo; 字，一句過，死唔斷氣，足足廿三個字。<br />\n好心啦。<br />\n人類係視覺動物。<br />\n一句句字，如果超過十五個字，見過咁撚長，已經唔想睇。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0bb961488035fe419a7b19bc5124becf4ce360f","tid":607889,"uid":7555,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T16:07:14.000Z","msg":"<del>表示</del>認同"},{"pid":"c92aa20bf3756b482e3287922646c95b89aebd9e","tid":607889,"uid":43976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T16:10:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aeb2eaeea7cf3a8cad8de9d348c337432930cc5a","tid":607889,"uid":178991,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T16:15:39.000Z","msg":"啱呀 至弊中小學都成日教歐化句"},{"pid":"4619a21f74ce442ebd0d42d37086af238f0dc9ff","tid":607889,"uid":93890,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T16:31:12.000Z","msg":"條友自己中文唔好又要教人中文<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d22cda6fa554f5c0d7f131148c0f38210d68760d","tid":607889,"uid":54337,"like":26,"dislike":4,"score":22,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T16:39:58.000Z","msg":"原句：<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">&ldquo;其實肥絲大隻的留言仍然白紙黑字存在讓大眾看到啊！&rdquo;</span></span></strong>(共23個字)<br />\n<br />\n上面講過，&ldquo;其實&ldquo; = 英文exactly。<br />\n縱使刪除句子入面嘅&ldquo;其實&rdquo;，都無損句子原本意思。<br />\n另外，老老實實，&ldquo;白紙黑字存在&rdquo; 呢六個字，太過地道香港口語。<br />\n肥絲大隻，自稱老師，竟然寫呢啲垃圾，我並唔意外，因為條友真係垃圾。<br />\n<br />\n如果俾我落筆，我會咁寫。<br />\n<br />\n重寫句子：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>&ldquo;肥絲大隻的留言仍然存在，白紙黑字，讓大眾看到。&rdquo;</strong></span></span>(共20個字)<br />\n<br />\n19才子有介紹一個猶太佬 (我忘記其名字) 教寫文章，書名叫 of writing (好似係，唔肯定)。書中教：感歎號無助表達感歎嘅意思，感歎號係廢，切勿使用。<br />\n<br />\n紅字原句好啲，還是綠字重寫句子好啲？<br />\n各位心中自評。"},{"pid":"de8bfae2cf6de0eb99b4bb97e1fe381d6aff6374","tid":607889,"uid":54337,"like":41,"dislike":0,"score":41,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T16:57:56.000Z","msg":"&ldquo; 沒有發言權利 &rdquo; (共6個字)<br />\n這一句垃圾中文，歐式到爆，不知所謂。well，我唔意外，因為肥絲本身就係垃圾。<br />\n<br />\n如果俾我落筆，我會寫：&ldquo; 無權發言 &rdquo; (共4個字)<br />\n<br />\nQuick and easy，又sharp 醒，搞掂，收工。"},{"pid":"7d4137c11ff098f9b9c0d476fc540c09fac5d380","tid":607889,"uid":78074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T17:02:50.000Z","msg":"無鳩啦啦名詞化晒啲動詞"},{"pid":"e568742590c67668b1215eb71d802456d391b880","tid":607889,"uid":63675,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T17:03:17.000Z","msg":"Exactly 解 正是<br />\nActually 解 其實<br />\n我想咁想翻譯得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdc19b44155c63d9df9945989abd2e6332ac2bad","tid":607889,"uid":54337,"like":9,"dislike":4,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"aeb2eaeea7cf3a8cad8de9d348c337432930cc5a","tid":607889,"uid":178991,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T16:15:39.000Z","msg":"啱呀 至弊中小學都成日教歐化句"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T17:09:47.000Z","msg":"中文垃圾教科書寫：&ldquo;歐化&rdquo;中文。<br />\n&ldquo;歐化&rdquo;中文，本身就是歐化中文。<br />\n<br />\n因為歐化 = europeanization。<br />\n所以我會稱&ldquo;歐化&rdquo;中文做&ldquo;<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">歐式</span></strong>&rdquo;中文。"},{"pid":"ca3da1e588f5016020718aaca891c61b5aaf1ed4","tid":607889,"uid":100150,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T17:22:42.000Z","msg":"你睇中國所有正式文書就知<br />\n全部歐式漢文"},{"pid":"53605ba3f770e84dc8076199f3119cda87a8a011","tid":607889,"uid":54337,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T17:24:12.000Z","msg":"仲有，掩耳盜鈴本身嘅釋義係：偷鐘唔想俾人聽到所以自己掩蓋耳朵。典出呂氏春秋。<br />\n<br />\n係偷<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">鐘</span></strong></span>。後世錯開，一直錯，先變左偷鈴。古人錯開，約定俗成，鐘變左做鈴。<br />\n<br />\n肥屍你張圖，咁撚大個鐘，你見唔到咩？你釋義仲係要寫 &ldquo;鈴鐺&rdquo;？"},{"pid":"abeef855f7936ce3e2e2b70bcb17956984993cfc","tid":607889,"uid":10998,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T17:34:38.000Z","msg":"對此帖文進行留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd7c51a8b9dad8694d960b63f98b2b107bbe856a","tid":607889,"uid":54337,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T17:35:18.000Z","msg":"原本應該係掩耳盜鐘，錯開，約定俗成，變左做掩耳盜鈴。<br />\n<br />\n肥屍同其黨羽，之前猛話，正字就係正字，錯就係錯，無約定俗成呢回事。<br />\n<br />\n你地可否解釋下點解肥屍張圖，大大隻字寫掩耳盜鈴，請問個鈴字，發生緊乜事呢？"},{"pid":"98c8dda7cef7657dfffce416c552cf5ff4bb4810","tid":607889,"uid":23829,"like":4,"dislike":17,"score":-13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T17:37:22.000Z","msg":"又一個想借肥絲上位<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"211dc21069d259b782c346e17b545cf9478529d3","tid":607889,"uid":118360,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T17:38:07.000Z","msg":"香港係用「」引號<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b26c3aab203c961a0e098869000f29ff6db1b519","tid":607889,"uid":118360,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"211dc21069d259b782c346e17b545cf9478529d3","tid":607889,"uid":118360,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T17:38:07.000Z","msg":"香港係用「」引號<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T17:38:40.000Z","msg":"當然o係 forum 又未必揸得咁正"},{"pid":"5bbb5870bfa5a2d3468885d7bcf2763557c6f3c9","tid":607889,"uid":159344,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T17:42:15.000Z","msg":"張圖係肥絲整嘅?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba842e5bcff260752d722bdf59ab761c0e2c4a64","tid":607889,"uid":54337,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T02:30:09.000Z","msg":"肥屍條垃圾，張掩耳盜鈴圖，仲可以俾人挖到幾多樣錯處出嚟？<br />\n<br />\n行家一出手，便知有無有。<br />\n<br />\n肥屍 = 垃圾"},{"pid":"e2eb2dbed0d3856473183263da61f35d0a80abdb","tid":607889,"uid":54337,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T02:38:51.000Z","msg":"哦，唔怪之得啦，肥屍條垃圾原來copy and paste 支那大陸殘體網站：<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/28/103808_3d0cf04f7570cc8255a73297735166dd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%